Covert Skins.name: P2000 | Fire Elemental
Covert Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with the image of a creature made of fire in a graphic style.
Covert Skins.lore: Sometimes playing with fire is a good thing

Covert Skins.name: AK-47 | Wasteland Rebel
Covert Skins.desc: It has been distressed, block printed, and painted with graffiti.
Covert Skins.lore: One day they will ask why we fight, and when they do they will understand - Naomi, Bodyguard to Valeria Jenner

Classified Skins.name: XM1014 | Tranquility
Classified Skins.desc: It has been hand painted with the image of a woman with long hair.
Classified Skins.lore: I'm not here for what I need; I'm here for something I want - Imogen and The Oni Part 2

Classified Skins.name: P250 | Cartel
Classified Skins.desc: It has been engraved with skeletons, flowers and serpents.
Classified Skins.lore: One little squeeze turns every morning into the Day of the Dead

Classified Skins.name: SCAR-20 | Cardiac
Classified Skins.desc: It has been heat wrapped with vinyl pre-printed in a modern orange and blue design.

Restricted Skins.name: Glock-18 | Grinder
Restricted Skins.desc: The steel slide has been painted using a combination of stenciling and hand-painting using oil paints.
Restricted Skins.lore: The only way to make diamonds is by applying pressure

Restricted Skins.name: Sawed-Off | Highwayman
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been lacquered in black and gold using a scotch thistle motif.
Restricted Skins.lore: You don't have to hold your pinky out when pulling the trigger, but it's a nice touch

Restricted Skins.name: M4A4 | Griffin
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been hand-painted with an illustration of a griffin.
Restricted Skins.lore: Felix handpicked his team from operators all over the world... and while people question their personalities, they never question the results

Restricted Skins.name: M4A1-S | Basilisk
Restricted Skins.desc: It has been etched with a basilisk.
Restricted Skins.lore: It's rude to stare, but war isn't the time for pleasantries

Mil-Spec Skins.name: UMP-45 | Delusion
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been screen printed with a nautilus design.

Mil-Spec Skins.name: Five-SeveN | Urban Hazard
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been custom painted with urban camo and red accents.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Every year, Booth gathers the worlds foremost designer gunsmiths to show off their latest designs

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MP9 | Dart
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been painted using a striped hydrographic arranged in a chevron pattern.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: Throw enough downfield and you're bound to hit the bullseye eventually

Mil-Spec Skins.name: G3SG1 | Murky
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been anodized then painted using a leopard-spot hydrographic.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: There is always some place darker you can go

Mil-Spec Skins.name: MAG-7 | Firestarter
Mil-Spec Skins.desc: It has been spray-painted in layers then distressed to give the appearance of burning edges.
Mil-Spec Skins.lore: It always begins with a tiny spark
